name: UpdateApplicationAirwayBill
xslt:
<xsl:stylesheet version="2.0" xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform">
    <xsl:template match="/">
        <UpdateAirWayBillNo xmlns="http://vision.emaratech.ae/">
            <CorrelationId xmlns=""><xsl:text>correlationId1</xsl:text></CorrelationId>
            <ApplicationNumber xmlns="">
                <xsl:value-of select="UnifiedApplication/ApplicationDetails/ApplicationId"/>
            </ApplicationNumber>
            <AirWayBillNo xmlns="">
                <xsl:value-of select="UnifiedApplication/ApplicationDetails/AirwayBillId"/>
            </AirWayBillNo>
            <Timestamp xmlns="">
               <xsl:value-of select="UnifiedApplication/ApplicationDetails/StatusDate"/>
            </Timestamp>
        </UpdateAirWayBillNo>
    </xsl:template>
</xsl:stylesheet>
